    Package Description
    de.budget.common
    Package for interfaces Package for the interfaces of the websercive.
    de.budget.dto
    Package for the data tranfer object Package with all data transfer object classes in it, which are needed for the datatransfer
    de.budget.dto.Response
    Package for responses Package with all responses, which are filled with the data transfer objects and a return code und a message

    Package for helper beans Package for helper classes, which are needed by the webservice.
